Package: metasignatures
Title: Analysis of Metasignatures on Perturbational Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ian", "Smith", email="ianc.smith@mail.utoronto.ca", role=c("aut"), comment=c(ORCID="0000-0003-3957-4397")),
    person("Benjamin", "Haibe-Kains", email="benjamin.haibe.kains@utoronto.ca", role=c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: This package contains code used to characterize the statistical properties of metasignatures (or consensus signatures) on perturbational datasets. It is the code base for the associated manuscript, "Similarity bias from averaging signatures from the Connectivity Map."
